s1.ptxt: Perform Steps 1) through 5) of DTC check procedure and have DTC indicated.
Close driver side door and within 10 seconds after that, perform Steps a) to c) described below.

s2.ptxt: Push unlock side (3) of driver side manual door lock switch (1).
Push lock side (2) of driver side manual door lock switch.
Repeat Steps a) and b) 3 times.
At the end of Step c), DTCs are cleared and key indicator light indicates DTC No. 12 (Normal).

s1.ptxt: After completing DTC clearance, remove ignition key from ignition key cylinder.
